BT /F1 15 Tf 0.051 0.078 0.094 rg 58 760 Td (3. What the system routes) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 0.051 0.078 0.094 rg 58 728 Td (The system should route work to the right person, agent, or tool.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 0.051 0.078 0.094 rg 58 705 Td (Not every task needs a model. Some tasks need a checklist. Some need a human) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 0.051 0.078 0.094 rg 58 690 Td (decision. Some need a known automation. The system earns its keep when it knows) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 0.051 0.078 0.094 rg 58 675 Td (the difference.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 0.051 0.078 0.094 rg 58 652 Td (Good routing reduces copy-paste work. It also stops expensive model calls from) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 0.051 0.078 0.094 rg 58 637 Td (being used as glue between badly connected steps.) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 0.051 0.078 0.094 rg 58 614 Td (4. What the system returns) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 0.051 0.078 0.094 rg 58 582 Td (Every meaningful action should return a receipt.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 0.051 0.078 0.094 rg 58 559 Td (A receipt is not bureaucracy. It is proof that the task was received, handled, or) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 0.051 0.078 0.094 rg 58 544 Td (escalated. It should make the status visible without forcing someone to hunt) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 0.051 0.078 0.094 rg 58 529 Td (through chats, docs, inboxes, and dashboards.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 0.051 0.078 0.094 rg 58 506 Td (If nobody can see where the work is, the system is not finished.) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 0.051 0.078 0.094 rg 58 483 Td (5. Where AI actually earns its keep) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 0.051 0.078 0.094 rg 58 451 Td (AI is useful where judgment, synthesis, language, prioritization, or pattern) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 0.051 0.078 0.094 rg 58 436 Td (recognition changes the outcome.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 0.051 0.078 0.094 rg 58 413 Td (It is much less useful as a substitute for basic plumbing. If the task is already) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 0.051 0.078 0.094 rg 58 398 Td (clear and repeatable, the better answer may be a rule, form, queue, or) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 0.051 0.078 0.094 rg 58 383 Td (notification.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 0.051 0.078 0.094 rg 58 360 Td (The commercial win is not "more AI." It is fewer dropped handoffs, less manual) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 0.051 0.078 0.094 rg 58 345 Td (transfer, and more time spent on decisions that actually matter.) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 0.051 0.078 0.094 rg 58 322 Td (6. A practical first step) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 0.051 0.078 0.094 rg 58 290 Td (Pick one recurring handoff that wastes time.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 0.051 0.078 0.094 rg 58 267 Td (Use four questions:) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 0.051 0.078 0.094 rg 58 244 Td (- Where is the work captured?) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 0.051 0.078 0.094 rg 58 221 Td (- Who or what decides where it goes?) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 0.051 0.078 0.094 rg 58 198 Td (- What action is expected next?) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 0.051 0.078 0.094 rg 58 175 Td (- What receipt proves it happened?) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 0.051 0.078 0.094 rg 58 152 Td (If any answer depends on someone remembering, searching, or copying from one tool) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 0.051 0.078 0.094 rg 58 137 Td (to another, that is the first place to fix.) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 0.051 0.078 0.094 rg 58 114 Td (7. CTA) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 0.051 0.078 0.094 rg 58 82 Td (Comment or DM "SYSTEM" if you want a practical way to find the handoffs wasting) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 0.051 0.078 0.094 rg 58 67 Td (time in your business.) Tj ET
BT /F2 8 Tf 0.169 0.184 0.196 rg 58 32 Td (Time to Revenue) Tj ET
endstream
